#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:concert_halls.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>\n"
"                        <span class=\"h2-fs\">\n"
"                            Tips for Success<br/>\n"
"                            <br/>\n"
"                        </span>\n"
"                    </strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>\n"
"                        <span class=\"h2-fs\">\n"
"                            Quelques conseils pour réussir<br/>\n"
"                            <br/>\n"
"                        </span>\n"
"                    </strong>"

#. module: concert_halls
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:concert_halls.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\"/></strong><span class=\"h5-fs\">Create your "
"events in advance and use early-bird tickets to generate interest.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\"/></strong><span class=\"h5-fs\">Créez vos "
"événements à l’avance et utilisez des tickets early bird pour susciter "
"l’intérêt.</span>"

#. module: concert_halls
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:concert_halls.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Accounting</strong>: Keep track of income from sales, donations, and "
"sponsors."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Comptabilité</strong> : suivez les revenus provenant des ventes, des "
"dons et des sponsors."

#. module: concert_halls
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:concert_halls.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Apps &amp; What They Do:</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Les apps &amp; leur utilité :</strong>"

#. module: concert_halls
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:concert_halls.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Attendance</strong>: Monitor registrations and scan tickets at the "
"entrance."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Présences</strong> : suivez les inscriptions et scannez les tickets "
"à l’entrée."

#. module: concert_halls
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:concert_halls.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>CRM</strong>: Track leads and partnerships with sponsors, agencies, "
"and groups."
msgstr ""
"<strong>CRM</strong> : suivez les leads et les partenariats avec des "
"sponsors, des agences et des groupes."

#. module: concert_halls
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:concert_halls.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Dashboards</strong>: Visualize performance with real-time KPIs."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Tableaux de bord</strong> : visualisez les performances avec des KPI "
"en temps réel."

#. module: concert_halls
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:concert_halls.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Email Marketing</strong>: Send newsletters and pre-sales to loyal "
"fans."
msgstr ""
"<strong>E-mail Marketing</strong> : envoyez des newsletters et des "
"informations de prévente à vos fans fidèles."

#. module: concert_halls
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:concert_halls.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Events</strong>: Create event details, schedule, tickets, pricing, "
"and reminders."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Événements</strong> : créez les détails des événements, la "
"planification, les tickets, les prix et les rappels."

#. module: concert_halls
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:concert_halls.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Events</strong>: Plan, publish, and manage concerts with "
"registrations and attendance tracking."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Événements</strong> : planifiez, publiez et gérez des concerts avec "
"inscriptions et suivi des participants."

#. module: concert_halls
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:concert_halls.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Get an instant overview </strong>: need to understand what needs to "
"be done? The Project Stages and Status icons give you an instant overview of "
"where things are at, and what needs to be prioritized."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Obtenez un aperçu instantané</strong> : vous voulez comprendre ce "
"qui doit être fait ? Les étapes du projet et les icônes de statut vous "
"offrent une vision immédiate de la situation et des priorités à traiter."

#. module: concert_halls
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:concert_halls.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Inventory</strong>: Stay on top of merch and bar stock levels."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Inventaire</strong> : gardez le contrôle des stocks de merchandising "
"et de bar."

#. module: concert_halls
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:concert_halls.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Link Tracker</strong>: Measure performance of your campaigns."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Tracker de liens</strong> : mesurez la performance de vos campagnes."

#. module: concert_halls
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:concert_halls.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Planning</strong>: Coordinate volunteers, bar staff, and sound "
"engineers."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Planification</strong> : coordonnez les bénévoles, le personnel du "
"bar et les ingénieurs du son."

#. module: concert_halls
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:concert_halls.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Point of Sale</strong>: Sell tickets and refreshments on-site with "
"real-time sync."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Point de Vente</strong> : vendez des tickets et des "
"rafraîchissements sur place avec synchronisation en temps réel."

#. module: concert_halls
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:concert_halls.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Project and Task Templates: </strong>Recurring tasks &amp; Projects "
"can be managed easily through the templates feature."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Modèles de projets et de tâches : </strong>les tâches et projets "
"récurrents peuvent être facilement gérés grâce à la fonctionnalité de "
"modèles."

#. module: concert_halls
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:concert_halls.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
